Emission spectra of CS-CPDs/LEV with addition of indicated concentrations of Cu2+ (a); the linear relationship between F0/F − 1 and CCu2+
                      (b); the effect of common ions (c) and sugars and amino acids (d) on the fluorescence signal (F/F0
                     ) of CS-CPDs/LEV/Cu2+ (The concentrations of all substances are 100 μmol/L).
